	   <tr><td colspan=2>I say just move on over to Qeynos newbie area. The yard in Qeynos is much smaller, so the MOBS are right there! In Tox the zone is pretty big and MOBS wander a great distance, so hunting is much more difficult there. Plus it's easy to get lost in Tox with all them big trees.<br><br>Hunt in Qeynos until you reach 4 or 5, then move into Qeynos Hills or Everfrost(I prefer Everfrost because you can get HQ Bear skins there) until 6 or 7, then head into Blackburrow and group up often. You can stay in BB until 15 easily.<br><br>PS. Keep all the Gnoll Fangs you get in BB and turn them in for EXP and a Moonstone to Captain Tillin on the balchony in the PVP area. Turn the Moonstones in for some alcohol to McJacubs(?) in the Fish's Ale.&nbsp;&nbsp;They are both in South Qeynos.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
