	   <tr><td colspan=2>Erudite is indeed a good choice. With any race a Wiz will still need to group at early levels.<br><br>It can be frustrating in the early levels, race does not change that. I have a Erudite Wiz at lv 6 currently in Everfrost peaks. He has died more than any of my other characters in their early careers. <br><br>I took the boat over to Qeynos and leveled up to 4 in the newbie yard before venturing to Everfrost. You can hunt in Blackburrow from 6-14 in groups, solo is very difficult, or group out in Everfrost fighting mammoth calves, polar bears, and snow leopards.<br><br>Qeynos has a Wiz Guild you can train at and buy spells from and the bank is in the same zone.<br><br>Arelin<br>lv6 Wiz<br>Torvonnilous<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
